{"tid":2446771,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★神秘組織座標曝光 ? Google Maps 出現大量神秘藍「M」標誌 !!","createTime":"2021-03-14T16:53:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T17:04:31.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8ea7e2d6a2cfd844664cfebf28a6e8a74dff8705","tid":2446771,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.xfastest.com.hk/2021/03/google-maps-blue-m-symbols-hong-kong_Cover.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.xfastest.com.hk%2F2021%2F03%2Fgoogle-maps-blue-m-symbols-hong-kong_Cover.jpg&h=24bf4931&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相信大家都有用過 Google Maps，不過大家有沒有發現最近在香港的地圖好像多了不少藍色的「M」字標誌 ? 到底這些「M」字是代表著什麼意思呢 ? M for「Mall 商場」?「Monitor System 監控系統」? 疫情爆發過的地標 ?  智能燈柱 ? 還是 Google Maps 意外曝光了某個神秘組織的據點呢 ?<br />\n<br />\n香港 Youtuber 現場親身勘探<br />\n<br />\n今日就有香港的 Youtuber 在探究這個神秘「藍 M」的答案。在影片中可見，他們在有「藍 M」的地點查看，最後發現每個「藍 M」所在地的共通點皆有 CCTV 監控。而他們亦發現在旺角的「兆萬中心」的「藍 M」標誌是最密集的，而且確實該地點亦真的發現不少 CCTV，他們亦指當年在所在的街道曾發生多宗高空擲鏹水事件，所以街道附近架設了不少「天眼」監控系統。難道這個「藍 M」真的是「M for Monitor System」?!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.xfastest.com/103016/google-maps-blue-m-symbols-hong-kong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.xfastest.com%2F103016%2Fgoogle-maps-blue-m-symbols-hong-kong%2F&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfFSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=fded0b5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.xfastest.com/103016/google-maps-blue-m-symbols-hong-kong/</a>"},{"pid":"d645121a6187e225a3518395e7fd01311021c8ab","tid":2446771,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2875678fb68b23daadbda03f763de46b992b4a6","tid":2446771,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:55:30.000Z","msg":"好似真係有鏡頭"},{"pid":"f05e357a91ee4761448373d11bc9dd72b0c099ee","tid":2446771,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:55:34.000Z","msg":"連登 -&gt; 公海 -&gt; 連登"},{"pid":"20800457b36bae66da7c9b97e83751d3d63dae6a","tid":2446771,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:55:48.000Z","msg":"連公連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca48f7b0e21c5f90ba90776f02d99549c339c28","tid":2446771,"uid":387826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:57:02.000Z","msg":"樓主來自潮州<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6bea841d1756fe3fea090a787f4f426365d8ae4","tid":2446771,"uid":148017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T17:04:31.000Z","msg":"一生愛潮爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}